reviewText: I have been "revisiting" a few of my VHS workouts by Cory Everson -- I sure do wish she'd put some of them on DVD!  Anyway, this workout is led mainly by Michelle LeMay, with Cory providing the "name brand" (she is a six-time Ms. Olympia) as well as form pointers, etc.  There is a third exerciser as well, and there is some bantering among them -- especially when Michelle refers to one of the moves as "sexercises!"  While the workout is definitely dated, it still provides a nice balance of both standing work and floorwork.
